nodes.text: Koedi Raef was a female member of the Alliance to Restore the Republic. She piloted a BTL Y-wing starfighter, on which she discovered a hidden data packet from the R2z Starship Maintenance Droid R2z-DL. It contained information relating to the Imperial presence in the Lifh sector and on the Vilosorian species. Using this data, Raef was able to facilitate the liberation of Vilosoria.
